Update for departments

UPDATE tbldep SET dep_name = [value-3], dep_desc = [value-4], dep_priority = [value-5], parent_id = [value-6] WHERE dep_id = [] LIMIT 1

Delete from departments

DELETE FROM tbldep WHERE dep_id = [] LIMIT 1

then delete all from tbldep where store_id is same as that of deleted one and parent_id = dep_id of deleted. Propagate this further on the children



